            <item>
                <title>利用Hugo构建个人网站-3：内容中转</title>
                <link>https://byteli.com/posts/%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8hugo%E6%9E%84%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99-3%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E4%B8%AD%E8%BD%AC/</link>
                <guid isPermaLink="true">https://byteli.com/posts/%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8hugo%E6%9E%84%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99-3%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E4%B8%AD%E8%BD%AC/</guid>
                <pubDate>Sat, 15 Feb 2020 22:51:26 +0800</pubDate>
                
                    <author>xwerthers@gmail.com (达达里昂)</author>
                
                <copyright>[CC BY-NC-SA 4.0](https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/deed.zh)</copyright>
                
                    <description><![CDATA[<h2 id="1-内容中转配置github">1. 内容中转——配置GitHub</h2>
<h3 id="11-向github同步网站">1.1 向GitHub同步网站</h3>
<p>这里我们使用cmd命令行工具，向Github推送我们的更新，现在还不用理解这些代码：</p>
<div class="highlight"><div class="chroma">
<table class="lntable"><tr><td class="lntd">
<pre class="chroma"><code><span class="lnt">1
</span><span class="lnt">2
</span><span class="lnt">3
</span><span class="lnt">4
</span><span class="lnt">5
</span><span class="lnt">6
</span><span class="lnt">7
</span><span class="lnt">8
</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre class="chroma"><code class="language-c#" data-lang="c#"><span class="n">e</span><span class="p">:</span>
<span class="n">cd</span> <span class="n">hugo</span>
<span class="n">cd</span> <span class="n">byteli</span><span class="p">-</span><span class="n">local</span> <span class="c1">//定位到博客根目录，对我而言，及&#34;E:\Hugo\byteli-local&#34;
</span><span class="c1"></span><span class="n">git</span> <span class="n">init</span> <span class="c1">//初始化git
</span><span class="c1"></span><span class="n">git</span> <span class="k">add</span> <span class="p">.</span> <span class="c1">//添加所有文件，最后有一个&#34;.&#34;，表示选择所有文件
</span><span class="c1"></span><span class="n">git</span> <span class="n">commit</span> <span class="p">-</span><span class="n">m</span> <span class="s">&#34;byteli&#34;</span> <span class="c1">//编写提交的备注，方便之后自己查看版本
</span><span class="c1"></span><span class="n">git</span> <span class="n">remote</span> <span class="k">add</span> <span class="n">origin</span> <span class="n">https</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="c1">//github.com/Celqaz/byteli.git //输入GitHub仓库的地址 
</span><span class="c1"></span><span class="n">git</span> <span class="n">push</span> <span class="n">origin</span> <span class="n">master</span> <span class="c1">//发出推送命令
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><p>最后一步向我们GitHub仓库推送成功的反馈结果大致如下：</p>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/02/15/OtMP3lGScK6CEds.png" alt="3.1master.png"></p>
<p>现在，我们再次打开GitHub的仓库页面，可以看到我们的项目已经成功上传。</p>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/02/15/HpJmaBbTuyjZF59.png" alt="3.2upload to github.png"></p>
<p>至此，我们就完成了本地网站的上传。</p>
]]></description>
                
                
                
                
                
                    
                        
                            
                                
                                
                                
